This device is unlocked from any phone company (factory unlocked).
The Xiaomi Redmi 9A 2GB/32GB 6.53´´ Dual SIM Smartphone is one of the most simple but functional designs of this brand since it has a basic camera, expandible storage with microSD, and an excellent battery, which makes it ideal for seniors or children.
This mobile phone is made with a MediaTek Helio G25 processor, with a CPU of 8 cores, which makes it fluid, with double SIM, 2 GB RAM, and a storage of 32 GB and expandible memory with microSD.
The MIUI 12 operating system, based on the Android 10, allows easy navigation with cleaned and well-organized icons. It comes with a 5000 mAh battery and has a capacity for charging at 10 W. It includes the main camera with 13 MP and a frontal camera with 5 MP. The display of this smartphone Xiaomi is 6,53” HD+ Dot Drop and resolution of 720 x 1600.
This mobile phone unlocked is compatible with 4G / 3G/ 2G /LTE /GSM/ CDMA network bands, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, GPS, radio, and includes a micro-USB cable. Its security system is protected by AI face unlock. Features:
Immersive 6.53´´ HD+ display: - The large display allows you to fully immerse yourself in the virtual world.
Low blue light for a comfortable viewing experience: - With blue light protection certification, your eyes will be at ease even after spending long hours on your phone.*
Massive 5000mAh Battery: - With 34 days of standby-battery time, this battery provides power that lasts.
